<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Under Construction</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        body{
    padding: 0px;
    margin: 0px;
    border: borderbox;
    background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    font-size: 100%;
}
.mainblock{
    text-align: center;
    margin-left: 50%;
    margin-top: 10%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    position: absolute;
}
.base h5{
    position: absolute;
    top: 47%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
}
.base h3{
    position: absolute;
    top: 75%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
}
.base p{
    text-align: center;
    position: absolute;
    top: 85%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    width: 80vw;
}
.ring1{
    height: 10em;
    width: 10em;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border-left: 1em solid green;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    z-index: 5;
}
.ring2{
    height: 10em;
    width: 10em;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border-top: 1em solid red;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
}
.ring3{
    height: 10em;
    width: 10em;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border-right: 1em solid blue;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    z-index: 2;
}
.ring4{
    height: 10em;
    width: 10em;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border-bottom: 1em solid yellow;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
}
.loading{
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    animation-name: loading;
    animation-duration: 5s;
    animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    animation-delay: 2s;
    animation-direction: normal;
}
@keyframes loading{
    0%{
        transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    100%{
        transform: rotate(2160deg);
    }
}
    </style>    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
    <div class="mainblock">
        <h1>Page Under Construction</h1>
        <p>developer is hardly working for publish the page</p>
    </div>
    <div class="loading">
        <div class="ring1"></div>
        <div class="ring2"></div>
        <div class="ring3"></div>
        <div class="ring4"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="base">
        <h5>404 error</h5>
        <h3>M Sri Sathish</h3>
        <p>touch the spinning wheel. then listen the song and be patient</p>
    </div>
    <audio class="audio1" src="/sounds/audio.mp3" hidden></audio>
    <audio class="audio2" src="/sounds/audio1.mp3" hidden></audio>
    <audio class="audio3" src="/sounds/audio2.mp3" hidden></audio>
    <audio class="audio4" src="/sounds/audio3.mp3" hidden></audio>
    <audio class="audio5" src="/sounds/audio4.mp3" hidden></audio>
    <script>
        var ntrack = Math.floor((Math.random()*5)+1)
        console.log(ntrack)
        const audio = document.querySelector(`.audio${ntrack}`);
        const loading = document.querySelector(".loading")
        window.addEventListener("load", function (){
            audio.play();
        });
        loading.addEventListener("click", function (){
        audio.play();
        });
    </script>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
